column3: “Perfection. Couchlock with bubbling euphoria and giggles. It's like OG Kush smacked you in the face with a designer bag. Get it!”
“LOVELY variant of OG Kush.  The 1/8th I laid hands on tested out at 30% THC content. A true one hitter quitter smoke.”

“Bred as a knockout high, Gucci was created to be smack-you-in-the-face strong. It is an award-winning strain, winning the 2013 Cannabis Cup for Concentrates. Gucci has a pungent, yet sweet flavor with a spicy aftertaste that is simply delicious: it is a very versatile strain. Great for social settings and acts like a sativa as it leaves you happy, tingly and energetic. When used at night it can allow you to relax eno...”

“Took some Googling to find out this strain is also known as Facewreck. And it does exactly that, in the best way possible. Vaped great; after one pack I was blitzed and the best version of myself with an idgaf attitude about it. Introspective yet extraverted, this strain will lift you whil keeping you mellow. Recommend.”

“Pretty quick come on that rushes the head. For how strong the speediness is, it’s relegated to the background / deep inside, which keeps it manageable. Mostly feel delirious. Clear eyed and energized like Jack Herer, but head is slightly dizzy - like on cold medicine. You’re there...but definitely stoned out. Feels tuned for socializing. Music is rich and unique sounding, but a considerable amount (40-60%) feels supp...”
“Its definitely worthy of the name. Very potent! I consider myself a heavy smoker, however this had me elevated after only a bowl.”
“The 1oz of this strain surprised me thoroughly. Potent? Yes. Aromatic? Very much so. Taste? One of my absolute favourites.”
“Great taste, very relaxing and damn good day time high. Definitely an good OG strain.”
“This is definitely one of my top favorite hybrids. It's a very happy high. Feel it both head and body. Taste is good. Overall a great high.”

“Pretty quick come on that rushes the head. For how strong the speediness is, it’s relegated to the background / deep inside, which keeps it manageable. Mostly feel delirious. Clear eyed and energized like Jack Herer, but head is slightly dizzy - like on cold medicine. You’re there...but definitely stoned out. Feels tuned for socializing. Music is rich and unique sounding, but a considerable amount (40-60%) feels supp...”
“Nice hybrid. Definitely high on the indica side.”
“Smokes well and is very tasty vaped also.  Wonderful oils in the mouth upon smoking with a wonderful taste.  Very social bud!”

“I just took a few tokes from my bong of this strain. It is fucking amazing! It's usually top-shelf but if you see this shit, by all means man...GET IT! 

Both the mind and body high are golden.”

“Hello dear people.  I just smoked a half a joint of Gucci Og, and I am quite high.  I feel elevated, with a Sativa-like pressure behind my eyes, and a suddenly carefree feeling about the phone call I must make in a half an hour.  A tough call, that now has been made easier through contemplation brought on from the inhalation of this fine flower.  I will go easy on the man I must chastise.
Nice taste; a little spicy o...”
“great strain taste, smell, high is excellent. What's difference between Gucci OG and Gucci tho??”

“FIRE HYBRID WHEN GROWN RIGHT AND CURED....FLOWERS } VERY STICKY AND DENSE WITH PUNGENT AROMA.SMOKE} VERY TASTY  BUT STILL A  HEAVY HITTER...HIGH} FELT BOTH EFFECTS OF ITS HYBRID GENETICS  STRONG ..SATIVA SIDE BEING THE FIRST TO SET IN WHICH WAS UPLIFTING AND ENERGETIC  FELT LIKE I GOT AN ENERGY BOOST...LOL...THEN 15 20 MINS LATER I FELT THE INDICA SIDE KICKING IN WHICH WAS VERY GOOD...  OVERALL *5 STAR SMOKE* FUCK WI...”

“Super high quality bud. The trichomes really stand out against the light green color of the leaf and smells of pungent sour citrus. The high is very uplifting and has you giggling just like any other OG strain. With a name like Gucci OG, this strain sure feels luxurious.”
“Hits hard fast. however it gives me the feeling like I really wanna do something but I just don't want to move. Fun for just chilling with friends.”
“One of the best strains I've tried ! Will surely get some more ..”
“WHAT is the Glucci strain? Yes. Glucci is what we call it. Earth, wind, AND fire. 10/10, relaxation and heat. Medicine.”

“Gucci one of the best strains I've tried in a long time very uplifting if your answer artist very creative strain wish I could find again it was a fluke the club by me had it they don't normally carry it but they need to get more if they can I would buy an oz or 2.”
“One of the better strains I had when in Denver. Very cerebral, and it had me and my wife giggling a bit. That also could have been the edibles. Anyway, very smooth and tasty!”
“Gucci is by far one of my favorite strains. It's under Indica but I see it as more of a hybrid. It's a happy high. Looks good, smells amazing and taste good.”
“🔥 relaxed body high and happy def couchlock tho but its 🔥”
“🔥 relaxed body high and happy def couchlock tho but its 🔥”
“Hits hard fast. however it gives me the feeling like I really wanna do something but I just don't want to move. Fun for just chilling with friends.”

“This strain had me very talkative and social which does not come naturally to me.  I loaded a bowl in my bong  before work and was in a very good mood for most of the day. Which again does not come naturally to me especially at work.  I highly recommend for anyone that suffers from social anxiety or depression. On a side note I member the smell and taste to be very pleasant.”
“Great smell, very dense, and frosty”
“I bought it at 10 a g it was amazing relaxing with a great head high. Flavour and smell are amazing if you get the chance give it a go.”

“I love this strain, probably my favorite strain. If I could buy a pound at a time, or if I could grow it myself I would. Anxiety, Depression, Stress, and Pain all gone. After a joint in the morning or mid day and I'm good for the rest of the day. The relaxation your body feels is amazing and long lasting, and it comes with a clear and happy head high.”
“HTC has some bomksi Gucci OG. The Way it's formed and the crystals are like heaven. The tast is between Butter-popcorn and Christmas Berry sprinkled on top!! It's not just anoth OG to over look!”
“Looks the part, doesn't smell the best but it has a great high effect and helps with my pain.”
“deeply relaxing and psychedelic...they cloned Gucci!”
“Great medicine! What PTSD?!?! Can you say happy?!!!!”
“the definition of $10 gram yhis weed can easily be placed in another dispensary and sold for 13 as top shelf but it isnt its a beautiful looking flower very sensual stench and nice colas”

“Tried this last night and wow.. If you are looking to relax and have that giggling feeling this is it.  Doesn't knock you out but great europhia feeling. I also found it to be quiet arousing as well. Def will get this one again.”

“Solid pain med..uplifting..Some OG taste and smell..nice head buzz! 
Good Choice”
“Decidedly a very social strain.  Works well when socializing.  Keeps you relaxed and stress free.   Sometimes on the sleepy side, but very brain awake.   Still helps with the pain.”

“Awesome variant to the good ol' OG Kush! Varying effects with different doses... It's much like smoking a top shelf sativa for the first few hits, then that Kushy Indica kicks in. Very tasty smoke. Extravagant and lavish body and head high.”

“This stuff is STRONG. I did one bowl of this and it put me out. Granted I did a larger dose on purpose because I wanted to go to sleep, but damn I wasn't expecting for it to hit me that strong and that fast. This strain is really really good, will definitely be going back to it. Only reason I'm giving it 4/5 is because it gave me really bad cottonmouth, other than that it's the perfect strain.”
“I LOVE this strain...its for sure one of my favorites..the smell, taste and especially the effects of it are nothing short of phenomenal.....🔥🔥🔥👍👍👍😤😤😤”
“This is great if you’re feeling down! I have energy and want to get things done. I highly recommend this!”
“It was really smooth but it made me really paranoid”

“Love it perfect splitting strain.  HIGHLY RECOMMEND.   
TRAVIS”
“Premium stuff there is a wonderful sativa onset that makes you feel great.  smell is very fresh quite earthy and some hints of sweet mixed in together.”
“Buds are crystal coated and light coloured. the high hits you very fast and tastes great. One of my favourite hybrids!”
“Love this strain! I've waited awhile for it to come thru at my fav clinic. Hits hard, and has a very nice euphoric high. Taste and smell is amazing.”
“great strain for those who want to relax and enjoy the taste of a fine Italian leather handbag .. cause it actually has a leathery taste!”
“Great tasting, great buzz!”
“not the tastiest or most pleasant to smoke but amazing effects”
“Wow 🔥”
